Create Table: Create a table to store flight data, including FlightID, DepartureDate, DepartureDelay, and other relevant fields.

sql
Copy
Edit
CREATE TABLE FlightInfo (
    FlightID STRING,
    DepartureDate STRING,
    DepartureDelay INT,
    ArrivalDelay INT,
    FlightTime INT,
    Origin STRING,
    Destination STRING
)
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
FIELDS TERMINATED BY ','
STORED AS TEXTFILE;
Load Data: Load flight data from a file stored on HDFS.

sql
Copy
Edit
LOAD DATA INPATH '/user/hive/warehouse/flight_data.csv' INTO TABLE FlightInfo;
Create Index: Create an index on the DepartureDelay column to improve query performance.

sql
Copy
Edit
CREATE INDEX idx_departure_delay
ON TABLE FlightInfo (DepartureDelay)
AS 'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.index.compact.CompactIndexHandler';
Query for Average Departure Delay: Find the average departure delay per day for the year 2008.

sql
Copy
Edit
SELECT DepartureDate, AVG(DepartureDelay) AS AvgDepartureDelay
FROM FlightInfo
WHERE YEAR(DepartureDate) = 2008
GROUP BY DepartureDate;
